data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
This is a full version of image processing package, the package contains implementations for the following algorithms:
Image Resizing Brightness & Contrast Arithmetic & Logic operations Quantization Convolution Average & Weight Filters Laplacian Sharpening Laplacian Edge Detection Gamma Correction Single Scale Retinex Histogram Equalization Histogram Matching Fourier Transform (Matlab installation needed) Ideal, Gaussian & Butterworth Low & high pass filters Gaussian Noise, Uniform Noise, Salt & Pepper Geometric Mean, Median, Min, Max, Mid-point Filters Adaptive Median Filter Periodic Noise Ideal Band Reject Filter Notch Pass & Reject
